---
title:  Ultimate Chicken Yaki Style Udon with Hoisin Sauce, Tenderstem®, Green Beans and Mushrooms
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This  Ultimate Chicken Yaki Style Udon is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R36_W19_UK_SU18947-4_Main_7_high-4cc35ba3.jpg
